    <title>java常用函数收录集</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/05/16/java%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E6%94%B6%E5%BD%95%E9%9B%86/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/05/16/java常用函数收录集/</id>
    <published>2019-05-16T11:08:21.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-05-18T07:21:25.523Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-获取当前月份的所有日期"><a href="#1-获取当前月份的所有日期" class="headerlink" title="1. 获取当前月份的所有日期"></a>1. 获取当前月份的所有日期</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * get all date of specified month(date format)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * <span class="doctag">@param</span> date</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">printDays</span><span class="params">(Date date)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Calendar calendar = Calendar.getInstance();</span><br><span class="line">    calendar.setTime(date);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// get total days of month</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> daysOfMonth = calendar.getActualMaximum(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// set 1st day of month,like 2019-03-01</span></span><br><span class="line">    calendar.set(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH, <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; daysOfMonth; i++, calendar.add(Calendar.DATE, <span class="number">1</span>)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(calendar.getTime());</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-生成指定日期段的每一天日期："><a href="#2-生成指定日期段的每一天日期：" class="headerlink" title="2. 生成指定日期段的每一天日期："></a>2. 生成指定日期段的每一天日期：</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> List&lt;Date&gt; <span class="title">listDays</span><span class="params">(Date startDate, Date endDate)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    List dateList = <span class="keyword">new</span> ArrayList();</span><br><span class="line">    dateList.add(startDate);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    Calendar startCalendar = Calendar.getInstance();</span><br><span class="line">    startCalendar.setTime(startDate);</span><br><span class="line">    Calendar endCalendar = Calendar.getInstance();</span><br><span class="line">    endCalendar.setTime(endDate);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (endDate.after(startCalendar.getTime())) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        startCalendar.add(Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH, <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        dateList.add(startCalendar.getTime());</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> dateList;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注：如果是指定时段的每个月，只需要将步进值的单位改为月份即可（<code>Calendar.DAY_OF_MONTH</code> -&gt; <code>Calendar.MONTH</code>），根据需要进行格式化即可。</p><h2 id="3-合并多个Map对象"><a href="#3-合并多个Map对象" class="headerlink" title="3. 合并多个Map对象"></a>3. 合并多个<code>Map</code>对象</h2><p><code>merge()</code>函数可以很方便的进行<code>Map</code>对象的合并。下面是将<code>map1</code>和<code>map2</code>合并到一个新的<code>Map</code>对象<code>midMap</code>中：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 从map1复制出一个新对象，用于存放合并结果</span></span><br><span class="line">Map&lt;String, Integer&gt; map = <span class="keyword">new</span> HashMap&lt;&gt;(map1);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 合并，key不变，value直接相加</span></span><br><span class="line">map2.forEach((key, value) -&gt; map.merge(key, value, (otherKey, otherValue) -&gt; value + otherValue));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4-List转Map"><a href="#4-List转Map" class="headerlink" title="4. List转Map"></a>4. <code>List</code>转<code>Map</code></h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Map&lt;String, Integer&gt; dateCountsMap = dateAndCounts.stream().collect(Collectors.toMap(DateAndCount::getDate, DateAndCount::getCount));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
